WEBVTT

00:03:59.200 --> 00:04:04.256
it could mean helping a mother
get treatment for her child

00:04:04.280 --> 00:04:05.696
suffering from malaria.

00:04:05.720 --> 00:04:08.536
Man: This is paracetamol.

00:04:08.560 --> 00:04:10.136
This is ACT.

00:04:10.160 --> 00:04:13.160
So the only time you're going to give it
is in the evening time.

00:04:13.184 --> 00:04:16.224
PP: In Liberia, the children
die more than the adults,

00:04:17.480 --> 00:04:20.255
because we have
some people in the villages,

00:04:20.279 --> 00:04:22.120
they don't sleep under a mosquito net.

00:04:26.000 --> 00:04:28.096
RP: We already know
community health workers

00:04:28.120 --> 00:04:30.776
can help health care systems
save more lives.